Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:09.83,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to restore my faith in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:12.96,club,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\an9}Let's start a competitive karuta club!\NPlease come see Ayase Chihaya in class 1-2!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:25.44,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have learned to both love \Nand hate my fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:31.72,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Swift waters parted by the jagged rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:34.46,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are joined at river's end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:56.72,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Waves creep closer to the Suminoe shore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:02.16,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in my dreams, I creep closer to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:10.46,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:17.52,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After many, many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.03,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look for the sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.41,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't beat Chihaya to the \Nfirst-syllable cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:29.20,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reassess the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.82,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Would this" was already read so \NI can take "Would the" on the "Would."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:38.49,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"My only thought as I" and "My only thought as the" \Nare both still in play, so I'll have to be careful there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.17,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"So the flower petals" was already read, \Nso I can take "So the flower has" after "flower."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.58,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Though my" was already read,\Nso I can take "Though I" after "Though."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.63,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For "While it pains", "While it may" was read, \Nbut "While it brings" wasn't, so I'll have to pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:54.02,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For "The hazy early morning light", \N"The hazy early morning mist" was already read,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.27,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so on "The hazy", I'll move towards \N"The hazy field" on the opponent's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.23,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"In the" and "In order to" have already been read,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:01:59.86,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I can take "In order for" on "In."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:06.25,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but instead you see a pale \Nmoon in the dawn sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:14.88,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order for us to find our way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:13.37,Chiha-card-TS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the plum blossoms still smell the same\Nwould I rather never seen her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.68,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya doesn't know how to make adjustments \Nbased on which cards have been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.62,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reacted first...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.35,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.08,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take the card...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:33.73,Chiha-title,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:43.00,Chiha-ep-title-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}But for \NAutumn's\N Coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:43.00,Chiha-ep-title-verse,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,800)}Verse 7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.09,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:52.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I should have passed you the "I know" card,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and then I should have waited before-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.96,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She just fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.10,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She just bulls her way through a match \Nby relying on her fast reflex time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.60,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I still can't beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.19,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In karuta, it refers to the speed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.71,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at which someone reacts to a card being read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Some people say it's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.17,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the most important quality \Na karuta player can have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.89,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was born with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya's karuta is driven \Nby that innate ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't have \Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:32.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.44,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's actually possible \Nfor Chihaya-chan to play in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:38.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Queen match wearing \Na hakama from our store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On national TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.59,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.80,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or would the violet one be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.80,Chiha-overlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of \Nbetter players in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.01,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This one looks better,\N but I should choose this one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if I want people to understand\Nhow wonderful kimono are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.45,Chiha-internaloverlap,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya and I are on completely different skill levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:59.70,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in becoming a Master,\N so I don't mind losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.27,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.18,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:15.65,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If Chihaya were to practice \Nwith Arata instead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:21.18,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would she become a better player?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.84,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go do some scouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scouting?  For a fourth member?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.75,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The second-smartest person in our \Ngrade, after Mashima Taichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun, who happens to be in my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two can practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.11,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:53.30,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need five members before we \Ncan become an official club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.66,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have enough members, \Nyou can't be a club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.65,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.62,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.09,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he creep you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,School's over and he's still studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that Tsutomu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He only leaves his desk \Nto go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.13,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he look like a jelly bean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.50,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.89,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many judgmental fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.23,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, solved that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.50,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, I like to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:56.36,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The harder I work, the higher \Nour class's average scores are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.49,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to help out those fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kinda sad when he's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.75,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,glued to his desk all day and \Nonly second in our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.00,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.89,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun from Class 1 is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't study much, \Nyet he's top of the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.31,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could arrange a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have a number one stud \Nthan number two Desktomu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.62,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!  I'm Ayase Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:34.40,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to scout you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play karuta together \Nin the karuta club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this a bribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.75,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Komano-kun.  You're the second-smartest \Nperson in our grade, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.30,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that karuta is a \Ngreat sport for smart people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you join, we'll have four members
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and be one member closer to \Nbecoming an official club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.68,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you \Ndon't have any experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.44,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, karuta as in Hundred Poets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.73,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any point to playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become number one by playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as \Nprofessional karuta, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.34,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.37,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I play this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.26,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will it help me with my studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.74,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any benefit for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.64,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:36.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop griping and play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:43.01,jam bread,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Jam Bread
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The field of play is supposed \Nto be 87 centimeters wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:52.09,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can use your elbow plus or minus \Na number of cards as a reference,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so remember how many cards \Nit takes to get you to 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.47,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.48,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Just come inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:09.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's teach him how fun karuta can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.16,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.19,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.13,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged me all the way here by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.88,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The karuta club is short on members, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you just need to bolster head count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look elsewhere, if you don't care who joins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.86,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I do care who joins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.38,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that you'll be hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I had time to play karuta, \NI would be studying instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.99,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-kun, you want to \Nbecome smarter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:46.78,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.53,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is a mental game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.49,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, you have to memorize \Nthe positions of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.62,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The fastest people can memorize all \Nof them in five- no, three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:01.22,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger memorization skills will \Nhelp you with your studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize the positions?\N  Of every card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:04.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.02,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most basic step!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.27,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.12,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.54,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.52,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.03,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.06,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.00,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima Taichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.16,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's had the top score \Non every monthly test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.92,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The players get memorization \Ntime, so hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.29,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The match will begin in 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.18,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.57,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Memorization is the most basic step, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.56,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If karuta players all have excellent memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:57.81,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to play \Nwith the cards flipped over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.22,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't Concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.70,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the cards get moved around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:05.87,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.19,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're given memorization time, \Nand you still can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:13.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing impressive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.45,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!  Don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.58,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give it a try, so wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:19.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this annoying brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.82,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said that we \Nshould look for someone smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.72,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.63,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never played karuta \Nwith the cards flipped over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.33,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.43,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.10,Chiha-note,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Mizusawa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.10,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.15,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will play in your stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.73,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Oe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.27,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Is it okay, Taichi?
