Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.12,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.45,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
