Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:06.51,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My own home is a retreat lying \Nsoutheast of the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the right card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.41,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.09,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized that card.
