Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.85,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:24.10,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because her memorization skills are still lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:31.71,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can beat Chihaya...
