Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:41.52,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's "No more, As friends, \NWhile it brings, As my, None are."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.06,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to move a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:43.50,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:44.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!  Hold on!
