Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.28,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was guarding both cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.57,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're over halfway through and he can still \Nremember the positions of the cards!
