Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:14.00,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as short-lived as the reeds of Naniwa Bay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:20.38,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in becoming a Master,\N so I don't mind losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.45,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.26,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the first frost has fallen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.64,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely hate to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.84,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.37,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one sitting across \Nfrom you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.79,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.31,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.55,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.31,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.61,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:48.07,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to leave without \Na word after that match?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.93,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.14,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.19,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.88,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,do people like him exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.65,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.91,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has friends, talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.41,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whose are those?  Desktomu-kun's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.07,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.30,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.29,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.01,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Desktomu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.98,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get the top \Nscore on the next test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.50,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The top score...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.32,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Become number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.94,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.65,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.40,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I do become number one,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.70,Chiha-internal,Default,0000,0000,0000,,they'll never let me in their circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:51.32,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're a little interested now, \Nwhy not join the karuta club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:06.01,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.76,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.36,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.42,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is study!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.77,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I belong behind my desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.27,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on contests that you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.79,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could spend my entire youth on karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.71,Chiha-flashback,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without ever becoming better than Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:49.26,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any talent for karuta either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.35,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough, but I still play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.51,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I keep losing, but I still play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.25,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because when I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.05,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so happy!
